Domain Decomposition MD (DdMd)
------------------------------

- Add readCommands() method to System to read a command file. 

- Write collector classes or methods, to allow writing configurations.

- Add Mask to Atom to allow masking of bonded interactions.
  Also add MaskBondPolicy to System, and code to update masks.

- Add potential styles and factories and clean up param file format.

- Add energy and boundary ensembles

- Port NVT and NPH integrators.

- Modify Exchanger to work ifndef UTIL_MPI, continue with other classes.

- Improve unit testing of CellList (add atoms and ghosts, small boxes),
  Integrator (check that number of interacting pairs doesn't change),
  System (test with very small system, 1x1x1 grid).

